Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:27.23,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,時々思う 気持ちが晴れる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:44.55,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,いつだってココが全てなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.47,0:00:49.72,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,雨だって綺麗に降ってるし
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.21,0:00:55.50,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,風の様に 踊れるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.78,0:01:01.00,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,今だってちゃんと楽しい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:06.61,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,リズムだって意外に持ってるし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:12.34,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,誰かの声 耳にしては
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.75,0:01:17.27,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,笑いながら 育んで来た
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.83,0:01:22.90,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,様な気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:28.89,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,そう帰る場所なんてもうどこでも良かったの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:34.31,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,さよなら太陽 いざなう様に夜が昇ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:39.61,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,大丈夫 世界は繋がる様に動いてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:46.28,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,もう一回もう一回 ちゃんと笑って会える様に
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----ED-----
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.21,0:23:48.81,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,手を切るくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:53.58,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,痛ッ!證明したい マイ存在自体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.38,0:23:56.93,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,永久ライン
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:24:01.67,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,囲い込まれても セーフティライン
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.16,0:24:05.15,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,「Wanna take you high ? 」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.42,0:24:10.11,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,揺れる銀河 君はスマイル
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.52,0:24:13.44,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,触れていたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.66,0:24:18.09,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,罰則なったとか 聞きたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.85,0:24:23.50,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,論にほだされ論理捨て
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.51,0:24:28.75,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,理性なきリスクゲームなど 申請
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.86,0:24:36.66,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,稀代の痛いのを以って 光彩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.05,0:24:44.96,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,実際とアン実際とをミステイツク
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.28,0:24:53.00,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,一切の理解の向こうに So Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.50,0:24:57.16,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,So Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.52,0:25:01.12,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,So Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.71,0:25:09.52,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,So Fight!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----TV-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从前 世上的诸多星辰混杂在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时人与神之间的界限还很模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这 是个围绕一家之间的爱与重生的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲…母亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我捡来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前说过喜欢孩子的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让这家伙做我们的儿子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是特别制作的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂他吃下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古都…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不是活人该吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别不小心咽下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在开始 这家伙就是我们的儿子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对我做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个家伙 是妖怪寺的和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们对我做了什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨天…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我捡来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你死了 所以我捡来把你复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经没有家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后就住在我们这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你呢 我希望能承担些儿子该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.64,0:07:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体怎么了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是死不了了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子… 不就成妖怪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这么泄气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键是习惯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很快就会有「活着真好」的想法咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为古都做的饭很香的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还真如上人所说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乐不思蜀的是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:40.88,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}注：对应第五集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我不觉得啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上的镜子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的母亲也有一个一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那个是怎么来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:11:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我借的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强行借的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是爸爸的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我十分想要 但他就是不给
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想要拿一件与妈妈有关的东西做护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师他想一人独占也太狡猾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我一直都称爸爸为老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真不太好改口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看看他长什么样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很帅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长得确实挺像的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛的颜色也很像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是年龄差太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太年轻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 老师的样子一直没变过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 有没有妈妈的画像?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大美女啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来八濑家里那张是妈妈的画像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她家可不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀 我根本没想到这人就是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 八濑和鞍马?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想利用你 你要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是鞍马
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是有个三长两短 我可是会很头疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…不过从这个角度上说 我跟他们也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 我很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我还没决定要杀你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无疑问 那孩子就是我们的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是或者不是 倒是值得试一试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为她破坏的东西 为什么不会恢复原状?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的那把武器 是叫「璞玉」对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据翔子所说 那个东西能引起一股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它和这里的东西再生时释放的力量一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可能和磁铁有点相似
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:15:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同一磁极的力量相撞 斥力就会把两者弹开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是当不同磁极互相吸引时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双方的吸力越强 它们就贴得越牢固
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的就一件事 就是你的话不知所云
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了验证一切的偶然 假设和推测
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想提议进行一项实验
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来次久违的钓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切顺利的话 你最珍视的妈妈就会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也将打开前往外面世界的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道会不会这么顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:16:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要行动才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来会变成一场热闹的庆典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「现在开始卖消灾的护符」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「明天不卖 只限今晚」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「虔诚的诸位请收下它 带它回家」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「请献上一根蜡烛吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「买一根蜡烛好不好?」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连香油钱都不舍得给 什么愿望都没法实现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:55.85,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}日语中有「地獄の沙汰も金次第」，\N即钱也能让地狱判官手下留情的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俗话不是说「有钱能使鬼推磨」嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来这里是地狱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 你不知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分啦 琴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿可是有鬼在的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有佛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八濑!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴 没想到你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在找我?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是逮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚才提醒过你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来迎接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.55,0:17:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来开始庆典的余兴节目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主角是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴!\N琴!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦——?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到「三人议会」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你们! 这怎么回事!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有需要 就会帮助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话 请你陪我们进行接下来的实验
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:17:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 慢着!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前从没提出过这个议题吧 我听都没听说过!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把规矩当什么了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是一而再再而三地破坏规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你却来提规矩? 明惠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 你可给我搞清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不太清楚情况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我该做些什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要陪它玩玩就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有任何意义的孩子有什么用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想期待你那像孩童一般的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常乱来的游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让毗舍丸做她的对手不正是她的心愿嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见啦 琴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没同意呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不承认这是议会的决定!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:18:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要服从「最初之人」和规定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:18:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞍马!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是正式的考试哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你其实是很清楚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你也是很想见妈妈的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「俄狄浦斯」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是要等得花儿都谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来这自主行动 才是重逢的关键呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.23,0:19:22.47,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(388,450)\frz3.394}是姐姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:22.47,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}称号 狼吞虎咽全收集\N随身物品 精神 香口胶 糖\N零用钱 两个人3日元
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:22.47,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(397,565)\frz4.096}出不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该会理解我们吧 琴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这事态发展很突然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过兄妹吵架 父母可是会伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思议呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家想见爸爸妈妈的心情明明是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是按捺不住想见妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 住手——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,固执的臭男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别碍着我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丫才是…到底在搞什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一直倍受各位照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不把我扣作人质我也愿意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会陪你们玩的 说好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这样不是不太好嘛 住持
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单方面把期待强加于人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我总是被大人背叛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来彼此都不太走运呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么认真干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像个白痴!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就让你丫闭嘴! 你这鬼!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是华丽的兄妹对打…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:57.25,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(375,497)}为什么搞不坏!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.93,0:20:57.90,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz356.178\pos(353,615)}他作弊。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.26,0:20:57.90,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(430,497)}用作弊器改角色太卑鄙啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下场挺不错的嘛 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的后继者!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 真是气死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这招如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:12.38,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(355,495)}上啊 琴!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:12.38,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(365,620)}做掉它——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.49,0:21:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊 明惠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个事情一直想问你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一张嘴就是抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却把那些孩子当成宝一样对待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之间是没有秘密的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 明惠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最舍不得的 到底是哪一方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见了吗 这精密机器!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必杀——家电破灭击!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白——痴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.86,0:22:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂停! 暂停!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.48,0:22:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是有点可惜啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.62,0:23:09.30,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(370,550)}让我们出去!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.88,0:23:09.65,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.15\frz359.191\pos(385,635)}让我们出去出去!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.30,0:23:10.00,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(390,550)}出去出去出去!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.65,0:23:10.40,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.15\frz359.191\pos(405,635)}出去出去出去出去!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.00,0:23:10.70,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(432,550)}出去出去出去出去出去!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:11.00,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.15\frz358.594\pos(446,635)}出去出去出去出去出去出去!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:11.00,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(477,550)}出去出去 出去出去出去出去出去!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 事情会怎么发展呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.12,0:23:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.64,0:25:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.24,0:25:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长得如此出落 妈妈好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.71,0:25:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉给你们留下了孤寂的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.92,0:25:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 也差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.82,0:25:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让那个梦变成现实
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.12,0:25:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.87,0:25:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 妈妈回来了 同时爸爸也回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.79,0:25:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一家人在一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.24,0:25:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要的仅仅是这样而已呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
